import React from "react"; import { Table, TableHead, TableRow, TableCell, TableBody } from "@mui/material"; function Transactions({ transactions }) { return ( ISIN Stock Name Quantity Date Type Total Cost DP Charges Other Charges {transactions.map((t, index) => ( {t.ISIN} {t.stockName} {t.quantity} {t.date} {t.type} {t.totalCost} {t.dpCharges} {t.otherCharges} ))}
); } export default Transactions;
